 Social Links Bar (Homepage)\";s:4:\"desc\";s:100:\"On the homepage, do you want to show social networking links? (Twitter, LinkedIn, Facebook, and RSS)\";s:2:\"id\";s:19:\"wp_showsociallinks1\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"select\";s:7:\"options\";a:2:{i:0;s:4:\"show\";i:1;s:4:\"hide\";}s:3:\"std\";s:4:\"show\";}i:169;a:6:{s:4:\"name\";s:36:\"Show Social Links Bar (Listing Page)\";s:4:\"desc\";s:123:\"At the end of each post, do you want social networking links? (Twitter, StumbleUpon, Reddit, Digg, Delicious, and Facebook)\";s:2:\"id\";s:19:\"wp_showsociallinks2\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"select\";s:7:\"options\";a:2:{i:0;s:4:\"show\";i:1;s:4:\"hide\";}s:3:\"std\";s:4:\"show\";}i:170;a:6:{s:4:\"name\";s:12:\"Show Search?\";s:4:\"desc\";s:31:\"Do you want to show the Search?\";s:2:\"id\";s:13:\"wp_showsearch\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"select\";s:7:\"options\";a:2:{i:0;s:4:\"show\";i:1;s:4:\"hide\";}s:3:\"std\";s:4:\"show\";}i:171;a:6:{s:4:\"name\";s:32:\"Show loan calculator (homepage)?\";s:4:\"desc\";s:56:\"Do you want to show the Loan Calculator in the homepage?\";s:2:\"id\";s:18:\"wp_loancalculator1\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"select\";s:7:\"options\";a:2:{i:0;s:4:\"show\";i:1;s:4:\"hide\";}s:3:\"std\";s:4:\"show\";}i:172;a:6:{s:4:\"name\";s:39:\"Show loan calculator (subpage sidebar)?\";s:4:\"desc\";s:73:\"Do you want to show the Loan Calculator in left sidebar of every subpage?\";s:2:\"id\";s:18:\"wp_loancalculator2\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"select\";s:7:\"options\";a:2:{i:0;s:4:\"show\";i:1;s:4:\"hide\";}s:3:\"std\";s:4:\"show\";}i:173;a:6:{s:4:\"name\";s:24:\"Show \'Compare\' checkbox?\";s:4:\"desc\";s:77:\"Do you want to show \'Compare\' checkbox on search results and Browse By pages?\";s:2:\"id\";s:10:\"wp_compare\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"select\";s:7:\"options\";a:2:{i:0;s:4:\"show\";i:1;s:4:\"hide\";}s:3:\"std\";s:4:\"show\";}i:174;a:6:{s:4:\"name\";s:43:\"Show comments form on Listing detail pages?\";s:4:\"desc\";s:66:\"Do you want to show the comments form on the listing detail pages?\";s:2:\"id\";s:23:\"wp_showcomments_listing\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"select\";s:7:\"options\";a:2:{i:0;s:4:\"hide\";i:1;s:4:\"show\";}s:3:\"std\";s:4:\"hide\";}i:175;a:6:{s:4:\"name\";s:38:\"Show comments form on blog/news posts?\";s:4:\"desc\";s:61:\"Do you want to show the comments form on the blog/news posts?\";s:2:\"id\";s:15:\"wp_showcomments\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"select\";s:7:\"options\";a:2:{i:0;s:4:\"show\";i:1;s:4:\"hide\";}s:3:\"std\";s:4:\"show\";}i:176;a:6:{s:4:\"name\";s:34:\"Show VinQuery tab in Theme Options\";s:4:\"desc\";s:182:\"If you will be using the VinQuery.com service to pull in VIN data into the detail page, then you will want to show this.<br /><br />Note: Reload this page after choosing this option.\";s:2:\"id\";s:15:\"wp_showvinquery\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"select\";s:7:\"options\";a:2:{i:0;s:4:\"show\";i:1;s:4:\"hide\";}s:3:\"std\";s:4:\"show\";}i:177;a:6:{s:4:\"name\";s:12:\"Show Footer?\";s:4:\"desc\";s:75:\"Do you want to show the widgetized big footer area? (above the footer menu)\";s:2:\"id\";s:13:\"wp_showfooter\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"select\";s:7:\"options\";a:2:{i:0;s:4:\"show\";i:1;s:4:\"hide\";}s:3:\"std\";s:4:\"show\";}i:178;a:6:{s:4:\"name\";s:27:\"Show the \'Related\' section?\";s:4:\"desc\";s:57:\"You can show related/similar listings in the detail page.\";s:2:\"id\";s:14:\"wp_showrelated\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"select\";s:7:\"options\";a:2:{i:0;s:4:\"show\";i:1;s:4:\"hide\";}s:3:\"std\";s:4:\"show\";}i:179;a:6:{s:4:\"name\";s:17:\"Show Contact Form\";s:4:\"desc\";s:46:\"Show Contact Form on each listing detail page.\";s:2:\"id\";s:18:\"wp_showcontactform\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"select\";s:7:\"options\";a:2:{i:0;s:4:\"show\";i:1;s:4:\"hide\";}s:3:\"std\";s:4:\"show\";}i:180;a:6:{s:4:\"name\";s:15:\"Show RSS button\";s:4:\"desc\";s:49:\"Show RSS feed button in social section in header.\";s:2:\"id\";s:10:\"wp_showrss\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"select\";s:7:\"options\";a:2:{i:0;s:4:\"show\";i:1;s:4:\"hide\";}s:3:\"std\";s:4:\"show\";}i:181;a:6:{s:4:\"nam